graph TD
    %% POWER SYSTEM
    Battery[11.1V LiPo Battery] -->|12V Power| Switch[Master Switch]
    Switch -->|12V| L298N[L298N Motor Driver]
    Switch -->|12V| Buck[LM2596 Buck Converter]
    Buck -->|5V Regulated| RPi[Raspberry Pi 3B+]
    
    %% MOTOR CONTROL
    RPi -->|GPIO 17/27/22/23| L298N
    L298N -->|Left Motor Output| MotorL[Left Motor]
    L298N -->|Right Motor Output| MotorR[Right Motor]
    
    %% SENSORS & VISION
    RPi -->|USB Port| Cam[Logitech C270 Camera]
    RPi -->|GPIO 17| IR[IR/PIR Sensor]
    
    %% NETWORK
    RPi -.->|5GHz Wi-Fi| Laptop[Laptop Control Station]
    
    %% STYLING
    style Battery fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RPi fill:#9f9,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px
    style Laptop fill:#9ff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px